(1, 1, '2016-06-03 13:21:40', '2016-06-03 13:21:40', 'Living Stream Ministry Podcast ::\r\nhttp://www.lsmradio.com/audio/stm-mp3/galatians/gal_22.mp3\r\n\r\nGalatians chapter 4 is a wonderful chapter focusing on two (2) divine sendings. God first sent forth His Son...but not only so,...He also sent forth the Spirit of His Son into our hearts. These 2 sendings in Galatians 4 are our topic on today\'s podcast.\r\n\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.lifestudy.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16\" src=\"http://jony5.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lsm_logo-1.gif\" alt=\"lsm_logo\" width=\"240\" height=\"200\" /></a>', 'Galatians chapter 4 is a wonderful chapter focusing on two (2) divine sendings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'two-divine-sendings', '', '', '2016-06-11 03:15:56', '2016-06-11 07:15:56', '', 0, 'http://jony5.com/blog/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
