(6, 1, '2016-06-03 15:05:23', '2016-06-03 15:05:23', 'Living Stream Ministry Podcast ::\r\nhttp://www.lsmradio.com/audio/stm-mp3/romans/rom_51.mp3\r\n\r\nSaints, the Bible reveals to us three (3) big enemies to our Christian life...sin, Satan and death. And all of these 3 take advantage of our fallen flesh to frustrate us, but God\'s approach to our flesh may surprise you. Check out today\'s podcast on the book of Romans for insight into our experience of dealing with the flesh and the secret of how to reign in life over these 3 enemies.\r\n\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.lifestudy.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16\" src=\"http://jony5.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lsm_logo-1.gif\" alt=\"lsm_logo\" width=\"240\" height=\"200\" /></a>', 'Saints, the Bible reveals to us three (3) big enemies to our Christian life...sin, Satan and death.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'saints-the-bible-reveals-to-us-three-3-big-enemies-to-our-christian-life-sin-satan-and-death', '', '', '2016-06-11 03:14:50', '2016-06-11 07:14:50', '', 0, 'http://jony5.com/blog/?p=6', 0, 'post', '', 2),
